#: src/reference/container.md:111
msgid ""
"**josh-proxy** - The main HTTP proxy service that handles git requests, "
"applies filters, and communicates with upstream repositories."
msgstr ""
"**josh-proxy** - 主要的 HTTP 代理服务，负责处理 git 请求、应用过滤器并与上游"
