msgstr "这些服务会在容器启动期间运行一次，以准备环境："

#: src/reference/container.md:120
msgid ""
"**josh-generate-keys** - Generates SSH server keys at `/data/keys/.ssh/"
"id_ed25519` if they don't already exist. Therefore, SSH server keys are "
