"服务器密钥，则生成它们。因此，当挂载该卷时，SSH 服务器密钥会在容器重启之间"
"持久保存。"

#: src/reference/container.md:123
msgid ""
"**sshd-generate-config** - Generates the sshd configuration file from a "
"template, applying configuration environment variables."
msgstr "**sshd-generate-config** - 根据模板生成 sshd 配置文件，并应用配置环境变量。"

#: src/reference/container.md:126
msgid "SSH access"
msgstr "SSH 访问"

#: src/reference/container.md:128
msgid ""
"Josh supports SSH access. To use SSH, you need to add the following lines to "
"your `~/.ssh/config`:"
msgstr "Josh 支持 SSH 访问。要使用 SSH，需要将以下行添加到你的 `~/.ssh/config`："

#: src/reference/container.md:137
msgid "Alternatively, you can pass those options via `GIT_SSH_COMMAND`:"
msgstr "或者，你可以通过 `GIT_SSH_COMMAND` 传递这些选项："

#: src/reference/container.md:139
msgid ""
"```\n"
"GIT_SSH_COMMAND=\"ssh -o PreferredAuthentications=publickey -o "
"ForwardAgent=yes\" git clone ssh://git@your-josh-instance.internal/...\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```\n"
"GIT_SSH_COMMAND=\"ssh -o PreferredAuthentications=publickey -o "
"ForwardAgent=yes\" git clone ssh://git@your-josh-instance.internal/...\n"
"```"

#: src/reference/container.md:143
msgid "In other words, you need to ensure SSH agent forwarding is enabled."
msgstr "换句话说，你需要确保已启用 SSH agent forwarding。"

#: src/reference/container.md:145
msgid "How SSH access works"
msgstr "SSH 访问的工作方式"

#: src/reference/container.md:147
msgid ""
"```mermaid\n"
"sequenceDiagram\n"
"    participant User as Git CLI<br/>(User Machine)\n"
"    participant Agent as SSH Agent<br/>(User Machine)\n"
"    participant SSHD as sshd<br/>(Josh Container)\n"
"    participant Shell as josh-ssh-shell<br/>(Josh Container)\n"
"    participant Proxy as josh-proxy<br/>(Josh Container)\n"
"    participant Upstream as Upstream Repo<br/>(e.g., GitHub)\n"
"\n"
"    User->>Agent: Load SSH keys\n"
"    Note over User,Agent: User's SSH keys remain<br/>on local machine\n"
"\n"
"    User->>SSHD: git clone ssh://git@josh:8022/repo.git:/filter.git\n"
"    Note over User,SSHD: SSH connection with<br/>ForwardAgent=yes\n"
"\n"
"    SSHD->>Agent: Forward SSH_AUTH_SOCK\n"
"    Note over SSHD,Agent: Agent socket forwarded<br/>into container\n"
"\n"
"    SSHD->>Shell: Execute git-upload-pack\n"
"    Note over Shell: Validates SSH_AUTH_SOCK<br/>is a valid socket\n"
"\n"
"    Shell->>Proxy: HTTP POST /serve_namespace\n"
"    Note over Shell,Proxy: Sends command, repo path,<br/>and SSH_AUTH_SOCK "
"path\n"
"\n"
"    Proxy->>Upstream: git fetch (via SSH)\n"
"    Note over Proxy,Upstream: Uses forwarded SSH_AUTH_SOCK<br/>for "
"authentication\n"
"\n"
"    Upstream->>Agent: Authenticate via SSH_AUTH_SOCK\n"
"    Agent-->>Upstream: Sign challenge with user's key\n"
"\n"
"    Upstream-->>Proxy: Repository objects\n"
"\n"
"    Proxy->>Proxy: Apply josh filter\n"
"    Note over Proxy: Transform repository<br/>based on filter spec\n"
"\n"
"    Proxy->>Shell: Serve filtered repo via Unix sockets\n"
"    Shell->>SSHD: Proxy git protocol\n"
"    SSHD->>User: Filtered repository\n"
"\n"
"    Note over User,Upstream: User's SSH keys never leave<br/>their machine. "
"Authentication<br/>is delegated through the<br/>forwarded agent socket.\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```mermaid\n"
"sequenceDiagram\n"
"    participant User as Git CLI<br/>(用户机器)\n"
"    participant Agent as SSH Agent<br/>(用户机器)\n"
"    participant SSHD as sshd<br/>(Josh 容器)\n"
"    participant Shell as josh-ssh-shell<br/>(Josh 容器)\n"
"    participant Proxy as josh-proxy<br/>(Josh 容器)\n"
"    participant Upstream as 上游仓库<br/>(例如 GitHub)\n"
"\n"
"    User->>Agent: 加载 SSH 密钥\n"
"    Note over User,Agent: 用户的 SSH 密钥保留在<br/>本地机器上\n"
"\n"
"    User->>SSHD: git clone ssh://git@josh:8022/repo.git:/filter.git\n"
"    Note over User,SSHD: 使用 ForwardAgent=yes<br/>建立 SSH 连接\n"
"\n"
"    SSHD->>Agent: 转发 SSH_AUTH_SOCK\n"
"    Note over SSHD,Agent: Agent socket 被转发<br/>到容器中\n"
"\n"
"    SSHD->>Shell: 执行 git-upload-pack\n"
"    Note over Shell: 验证 SSH_AUTH_SOCK<br/>是有效 socket\n"
"\n"
"    Shell->>Proxy: HTTP POST /serve_namespace\n"
"    Note over Shell,Proxy: 发送命令、仓库路径<br/>和 SSH_AUTH_SOCK 路径\n"
"\n"
"    Proxy->>Upstream: git fetch（通过 SSH）\n"
"    Note over Proxy,Upstream: 使用转发的 SSH_AUTH_SOCK<br/>进行认证\n"
"\n"
"    Upstream->>Agent: 通过 SSH_AUTH_SOCK 认证\n"
"    Agent-->>Upstream: 使用用户密钥签名挑战\n"
"\n"
"    Upstream-->>Proxy: 仓库对象\n"
"\n"
"    Proxy->>Proxy: 应用 josh 过滤器\n"
"    Note over Proxy: 基于过滤器规格<br/>转换仓库\n"
"\n"
"    Proxy->>Shell: 通过 Unix socket 提供过滤后的仓库\n"
"    Shell->>SSHD: 代理 git 协议\n"
"    SSHD->>User: 过滤后的仓库\n"
"\n"
"    Note over User,Upstream: 用户的 SSH 密钥永不离开<br/>其机器。认证通过<br/>转发的 agent socket<br/>委托完成。\n"
"```"

#: src/reference/container.md:189
msgid ""
"**SSH Agent Forwarding**: The user's SSH agent socket is forwarded into the "
"container, allowing josh-proxy to authenticate to upstream repositories "
"without accessing the user's private keys directly."
msgstr ""
"**SSH Agent Forwarding**：用户的 SSH agent socket 会被转发到容器中，使 "
"josh-proxy 能够在不直接访问用户私钥的情况下向上游仓库认证。"

#: src/reference/container.md:191
msgid ""
"**Two-stage architecture**: `sshd` handles the SSH connection and launches "
"`josh-ssh-shell`, which then communicates with `josh-proxy` via HTTP."
msgstr ""
"**两阶段架构**：`sshd` 处理 SSH 连接并启动 `josh-ssh-shell`，后者再通过 HTTP "
"与 `josh-proxy` 通信。"

#: src/reference/container.md:193
msgid ""
"**Security**: Private SSH keys never enter the container. All authentication "
"is performed by delegating to the user's local SSH agent through the "
"forwarded socket."
msgstr ""
"**安全性**：SSH 私钥永远不会进入容器。所有认证都通过转发的 socket 委托给用户"
"本地 SSH agent 完成。"

