#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:3
msgid ""
"`josh compose run` is an experimental `josh` CLI subcommand that runs "
"workspaces in isolated, automatically-cached containers. It is used to build "
"the josh binaries and run the integration test suite."
msgstr ""
"`josh compose run` 是一个实验性的 `josh` CLI 子命令，用于在隔离且自动缓存的"
"容器中运行 workspace。它用于构建 josh 二进制文件并运行集成测试套件。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:7
msgid ""
"**Note:** `josh compose run` is experimental and requires "
"`JOSH_EXPERIMENTAL_FEATURES=1` to be set in the environment."
msgstr "**注意：** `josh compose run` 是实验性的，需要在环境中设置 `JOSH_EXPERIMENTAL_FEATURES=1`。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:10
msgid "Motivation"
msgstr "动机"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:12
msgid ""
"A common problem with monorepo builds is that the container context contains "
"the entire repository — thousands of files most builds don't need. This has "
"two consequences:"
msgstr ""
"monorepo 构建中的一个常见问题是，容器上下文包含整个仓库——其中有成千上万个大多"
"数构建并不需要的文件。这会带来两个后果："

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:14
msgid ""
"**Fragile caching.** Docker and podman derive cache tags from the context "
"contents. Any file touched anywhere in the repo can break the cache even if "
"the build doesn't use that file."
msgstr ""
"**脆弱的缓存。** Docker 和 podman 会根据上下文内容派生缓存标签。仓库中任何"
"位置的任何文件被修改，都可能破坏缓存，即使构建并不使用该文件。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:15
msgid ""
"**Hidden dependencies.** If a build silently reads a file that \"happens to "
"be there\", it works locally but may break in a clean environment or for "
"another team member."
msgstr ""
"**隐藏依赖。** 如果构建静默读取了某个\"恰好在那里\"的文件，它可能在本地可用，"
"但在干净环境中或其他团队成员那里失败。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:17
msgid ""
"`josh compose run` addresses both problems by filtering the repository to "
"exactly the files a given workspace needs before any container is involved:"
msgstr ""
"`josh compose run` 会在涉及任何容器之前，将仓库过滤为给定 workspace 所需的"
"精确文件集合，从而解决这两个问题："

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:19
msgid ""
"The filtered tree's git SHA becomes the cache key. Only changes to files "
"actually included in the workspace invalidate the cache."
msgstr "过滤后 tree 的 git SHA 会成为缓存键。只有实际包含在 workspace 中的文件变更才会使缓存失效。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:20
msgid ""
"The container sees only what the workspace definition explicitly includes — "
"files outside the workspace are structurally impossible to access."
msgstr "容器只能看到 workspace 定义显式包含的内容——workspace 外的文件在结构上无法访问。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:21
msgid ""
"The host working tree is never modified. Artifacts produced by the container "
"are stored in a podman volume and exported back when the run completes."
msgstr "主机工作树永远不会被修改。容器生成的产物会存储在 podman 卷中，并在运行完成后导出回来。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:23
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "前置条件"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:25
msgid "**podman** installed and on `$PATH`"
msgstr "已安装 **podman**，并且位于 `$PATH` 中"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:26
msgid "**josh** installed and on `$PATH`:"
msgstr "已安装 **josh**，并且位于 `$PATH` 中："

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:27
msgid "`JOSH_EXPERIMENTAL_FEATURES=1` set in your environment"
msgstr "你的环境中已设置 `JOSH_EXPERIMENTAL_FEATURES=1`"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:33
msgid "Quick start"
msgstr "快速开始"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:35
msgid "All commands are run from the root of the josh repository."
msgstr "所有命令都从 josh 仓库根目录运行。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:37
msgid "Run all tests"
msgstr "运行所有测试"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:43
msgid ""
"With no arguments, `josh compose run` looks for a `compose.josh` file in the "
"repository root and uses it as the filter. In this repo, `compose.josh` "
"points to `ws/test.josh`, so `josh compose run` runs the full test suite."
msgstr ""
"不带参数时，`josh compose run` 会在仓库根目录查找 `compose.josh` 文件，并将其"
"用作过滤器。在此仓库中，`compose.josh` 指向 `ws/test.josh`，因此 `josh compose "
"run` 会运行完整测试套件。"

