msgid "Run a specific workspace"
msgstr "运行特定 workspace"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:51
msgid "Use the staged index instead of the working tree"
msgstr "使用暂存索引而不是工作树"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:57
