#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:123
msgid "Cache behavior"
msgstr "缓存行为"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:125
msgid ""
"Each run produces a podman volume named `out_<WS_TREE>`. Successful runs are "
"also recorded under `.josh/success/<WS_TREE>`. A cached result is reused "
"only when that success marker is present and, for workspaces that keep "
"output, the matching `out_<WS_TREE>` volume still exists. The cache key is "
"the git SHA of the filtered workspace tree, so:"
msgstr ""
"每次运行都会生成名为 `out_<WS_TREE>` 的 podman 卷。成功运行也会记录在 "
"`.josh/success/<WS_TREE>` 下。只有当该成功标记存在，并且对于保留输出的 "
"workspace，匹配的 `out_<WS_TREE>` 卷仍然存在时，才会复用缓存结果。缓存键是"
"过滤后 workspace tree 的 git SHA，因此："

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:127
msgid ""
"Changing any file included in the workspace automatically produces a new SHA "
"and bypasses the cache."
msgstr "更改 workspace 中包含的任何文件都会自动生成新的 SHA 并绕过缓存。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:128
msgid "Changing unrelated files has no effect on the cache."
msgstr "更改无关文件不会影响缓存。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:129
msgid ""
"Two developers with identical workspace contents share the same cache key "
"(useful if volumes are shared via a registry)."
msgstr "两个 workspace 内容相同的开发者会共享同一个缓存键（如果通过 registry 共享卷，这会很有用）。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:131
msgid "Forcing a re-run"
msgstr "强制重新运行"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:133
msgid ""
"To re-run without changing source files, remove the output volume manually:"
msgstr "要在不更改源文件的情况下重新运行，请手动移除输出卷："

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:136
msgid "# Find the relevant volume\n"
msgstr "# 查找相关卷\n"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:138
msgid "# Remove it\n"
msgstr "# 移除它\n"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:143
msgid ""
"Alternatively, use `josh compose run --clean` to remove all cached images "
"and output volumes, or `--clean-all` to also remove persistent cache volumes "
"(e.g. the Cargo registry cache)."
msgstr ""
"或者，使用 `josh compose run --clean` 移除所有缓存镜像和输出卷，或使用 "
"`--clean-all` 同时移除持久缓存卷（例如 Cargo registry 缓存）。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:145
msgid "Clearing all output volumes"
msgstr "清理所有输出卷"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:148
msgid "'^out_'"
msgstr "'^out_'"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:151
msgid "Workspace definitions"
msgstr "Workspace 定义"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:153
msgid ""
"A workspace is defined by a `.josh` file, typically under `ws/`. The file "
"uses josh filter expressions to declare what the workspace needs and how to "
"run it."
msgstr ""
"workspace 由一个 `.josh` 文件定义，通常位于 `ws/` 下。该文件使用 josh 过滤器"
"表达式声明 workspace 需要什么以及如何运行。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:155
msgid "Workspace keys"
msgstr "Workspace 键"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:157
msgid "Key"
msgstr "键"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:157
msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "用途"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:159
msgid "`:#image[:+path/to/image]`"
msgstr "`:#image[:+path/to/image]`"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:159
msgid "Container image workspace to build from"
msgstr "用于构建的容器镜像 workspace"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:160
msgid "`:$label=\"...\"`"
msgstr "`:$label=\"...\"`"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:160
msgid "Human-readable label shown in output"
msgstr "输出中显示的人类可读标签"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:161
msgid "`:$cmd=\"...\"`"
msgstr "`:$cmd=\"...\"`"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:161
msgid "Command to run inside the container"
msgstr "要在容器内运行的命令"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:162
msgid "`:$cache=\"name\"`"
msgstr "`:$cache=\"name\"`"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:162
msgid ""
"Persistent podman volume mounted at `/opt/cache` (e.g. for Cargo's registry)"
msgstr "挂载在 `/opt/cache` 的持久 podman 卷（例如用于 Cargo registry）"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:163
msgid "`:$output=\"none\"`"
msgstr "`:$output=\"none\"`"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:163
msgid "Disable output volume (run produces no extracted artifacts)"
msgstr "禁用输出卷（运行不会生成可提取产物）"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:164
msgid "`:$network=\"host\"`"
msgstr "`:$network=\"host\"`"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:164
msgid "Container network mode"
msgstr "容器网络模式"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:165
msgid "`worktree = :[...]`"
msgstr "`worktree = :[...]`"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:165
msgid "Files placed in the container's working directory"
msgstr "放入容器工作目录的文件"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:166
msgid "`inputs = :[...]`"
msgstr "`inputs = :[...]`"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:166
msgid ""
"Dependency workspaces; each named entry is run first and its output is "
"mounted inside the container"
msgstr "依赖 workspace；每个命名条目会先运行，其输出会挂载到容器内"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:167
msgid "`env = :[...]`"
msgstr "`env = :[...]`"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:167
msgid "Environment variables injected into the container"
msgstr "注入容器的环境变量"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:169
msgid "Example: `ws/fetch.josh`"
msgstr "示例：`ws/fetch.josh`"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:171
msgid ""
"```\n"
":$label=\"cargo fetch\"\n"
":#image[:+images/dev-local]\n"
":$cache=\"rust\"\n"
":$network=\"host\"\n"
"\n"
":$cmd=\"cargo fetch --locked\"\n"
"\n"
"worktree = :[\n"
"    ::**/Cargo.toml\n"
"    ::**/Cargo.lock\n"
"    ::**/rust-toolchain.toml\n"
"    ::**/lib.rs\n"
"    ::**/main.rs\n"
"]\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```\n"
":$label=\"cargo fetch\"\n"
":#image[:+images/dev-local]\n"
":$cache=\"rust\"\n"
":$network=\"host\"\n"
"\n"
":$cmd=\"cargo fetch --locked\"\n"
"\n"
"worktree = :[\n"
"    ::**/Cargo.toml\n"
"    ::**/Cargo.lock\n"
"    ::**/rust-toolchain.toml\n"
"    ::**/lib.rs\n"
"    ::**/main.rs\n"
"]\n"
"```"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:188
msgid ""
"This workspace fetches Cargo dependencies into a persistent cache volume. "
"Only the files needed to resolve the dependency graph are included, so the "
"cache is invalidated only when those files change."
msgstr ""
"此 workspace 会将 Cargo 依赖获取到持久缓存卷中。它只包含解析依赖图所需的文件，"
"因此只有这些文件发生变化时缓存才会失效。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:190
msgid "Example: `ws/build-rust.josh`"
msgstr "示例：`ws/build-rust.josh`"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:192
msgid ""
"```\n"
":$label=\"rust build\"\n"
":#image[:+images/dev-local]\n"
":$cache=\"rust\"\n"
"\n"
"inputs = :[\n"
"    :#fetch[:+ws/fetch]\n"
"]\n"
"\n"
"env = :[\n"
"    ::JOSH_VERSION=VERSION_STRING\n"
"]\n"
"\n"
"worktree = :[\n"
"    ::run.sh=ws/build-rust.sh\n"
"    ::Cargo.toml\n"
"    ::Cargo.lock\n"
"    ::rust-toolchain.toml\n"
"    ::josh-*/\n"
"    ::forges/\n"
"]\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```\n"
":$label=\"rust build\"\n"
":#image[:+images/dev-local]\n"
":$cache=\"rust\"\n"
"\n"
"inputs = :[\n"
"    :#fetch[:+ws/fetch]\n"
"]\n"
"\n"
"env = :[\n"
"    ::JOSH_VERSION=VERSION_STRING\n"
"]\n"
"\n"
"worktree = :[\n"
"    ::run.sh=ws/build-rust.sh\n"
"    ::Cargo.toml\n"
"    ::Cargo.lock\n"
"    ::rust-toolchain.toml\n"
"    ::josh-*/\n"
"    ::forges/\n"
"]\n"
"```"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:215
msgid "This workspace:"
msgstr "此 workspace："

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:216
msgid ""
"Declares `ws/fetch` as an input dependency; its output (the populated Cargo "
"cache) is mounted before the build runs."
msgstr "声明 `ws/fetch` 为输入依赖；其输出（已填充的 Cargo 缓存）会在构建运行前挂载。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:217
msgid ""
"Injects the `JOSH_VERSION` environment variable from the `VERSION_STRING` "
"file."
msgstr "从 `VERSION_STRING` 文件注入 `JOSH_VERSION` 环境变量。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:218
msgid ""
"Places `ws/build-rust.sh` into the container as `run.sh` (the entrypoint)."
msgstr "将 `ws/build-rust.sh` 作为 `run.sh`（入口点）放入容器。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:219
msgid "Includes only the source trees needed to compile."
msgstr "仅包含编译所需的源 tree。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:221
msgid "Creating a new workspace"
msgstr "创建新的 workspace"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:223
msgid ""
"**Write a `.josh` file** under `ws/`. Declare at minimum an `:#image[...]` "
"reference and a `worktree` subtree containing the files your build needs."
msgstr ""
"在 `ws/` 下**编写 `.josh` 文件**。至少声明一个 `:#image[...]` 引用，以及一个"
"包含构建所需文件的 `worktree` 子 tree。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:225
msgid ""
"**Write the entrypoint** either as a `run.sh` in the worktree or via `:"
"$cmd=\"...\"`. Place any outputs you want extracted under `/out` inside the "
"container (unless `:$output=\"none\"`)."
msgstr ""
"**编写入口点**，可以是在 worktree 中的 `run.sh`，也可以通过 `:$cmd=\"...\"` "
"指定。将任何想提取的输出放到容器内的 `/out` 下（除非 `:$output=\"none\"`）。"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:227
msgid "**Run it:**"
msgstr "**运行它：**"

#: src/contributing/josh-run.md:233
msgid ""
"**Add dependencies** via `inputs = :[...]` if your workspace needs the "
"output of another workspace. Each named entry in `inputs` is run first and "
"its output volume is mounted at `/<name>` inside the container."
msgstr ""
"如果你的 workspace 需要另一个 workspace 的输出，请通过 `inputs = :[...]` **添加"
"依赖**。`inputs` 中的每个命名条目都会先运行，其输出卷会挂载到容器内的 `/<name>`。"
